<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <!--Meta Tags-->
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
        <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.0-beta2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-BmbxuPwQa2lc/FVzBcNJ7UAyJxM6wuqIj61tLrc4wSX0szH/Ev+nYRRuWlolflfl" crossorigin="anonymous">        
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/index.css">
        <title><%= bot.name %></title>    
    </head>
    <body>
        <!--HEADER-->
        <%- include('header'); -%>
        
        <!--MAIN BODY-->
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center head">
            <h1><b>Easily enhance your Discord server!</b></h1>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center subtext">
            <p>Helpsie™ is a powerful multipurpose bot with features varying from moderation to leveling</p>
        </div>

        <div class="container custom-1">
            <img class="custom-image" src="https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/829674465872183336/829678327539171358/unknown.png">
            <h3 class="align-self-start"><b>Welcome Message and Role</b></h3>
            <p>
                Setup Helpsie™'s welcome system in the channel of your choice with customization of a unique welcome message and the option to choose a welcome role to be given to new members.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="container pt-10 custom-2">
            <img src="https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/829674465872183336/829680097204240394/unknown.png">
            <h3><b>Leveling System</b></h3>
            <p>
                Helpsie™'s leveling system allows you to create competition and engagement on your Discord with the help of level roles which you can easily setup to give members certain roles when they reach the required level, as well as a leaderboard to display the top achieving members.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="container custom-1 pt-16">
            <img class="custom-image" src="https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/829674465872183336/829681852087926794/unknown.png">
            <h3 class="align-self-start"><b>Advanced Moderation</b></h3>
            <p>
                Easily block profanity and links with Helpsie™'s Automod, ban, kick, mute and warn members with commands as well as set up Autmod Actions to automatically mute, kick or ban members when they reach a certain number of warns.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="container pt-10 custom-2">
            <img src="https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/829674465872183336/829697230667513856/unknown.png">
            <h3><b>Utility Commands</b></h3>
            <p>
                Helpsie™ provides many useful utility commands to use around your server such as a YouTube search, a user information command, a Covid-19 stats command and an urban dictionary command to search the meaning of that word you're stuck on!
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="container custom-1 pt-16">
            <img class="custom-image" src="https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/829674465872183336/829698278459310090/unknown.png">
            <h3 class="align-self-start"><b>Advanced Settings and Customization</b></h3>
            <p>
                Helpsie™ provides admins with a wide variety of customizable settings to ensure the needs of your Discord server are thoroughly met. When you first add Helpsie™ to your server, it's simple to use the setup process to tweak features to your liking!
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="container pt-10 custom-2">
            <img src="https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/829674465872183336/829698583866507274/unknown.png">
            <h3><b>Birthday Reminders</b></h3>
            <p>
                Helpsie™'s birthday reminder system ensures that you don't miss anyone's special day! Members can add and remove their own birthdays or admins can manage this for them. You can customize a birthday message, birthday message channel and a role to give on birthdays.
            </p>
        </div>
        <footer></footer>
        

       <!--JS-->
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.0-beta2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-b5kHyXgcpbZJO/tY9Ul7kGkf1S0CWuKcCD38l8YkeH8z8QjE0GmW1gYU5S9FOnJ0" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    </body>
</html>
